General.Name: Golden Long Teng Development Co Ltd
General.Description: Golden Long Teng Development Co., Ltd. engages in the development, sale, and lease of residential buildings. The company was formerly known as AME, Inc. and changed its name to Golden Long Teng Development Co., Ltd. in July 2016. Golden Long Teng Development Co., Ltd. was founded in 2000 and is based in Kaohsiung, Taiwan.
